description.p:
According to an aspect, a method comprises:
receiving, by a mobile device, radio frequency (RF) signals from a plurality of RF sources;
determining information associated with the plurality of RF sources;
comparing the determined information with a priori information associated with a set of indoor-only RF sources; and
determining whether the plurality of RF sources include at least one of the set of indoor-only RF sources.

According to an aspect, an article of manufacture is provided including a computer-readable storage medium having instructions stored thereon, execution of which by a computing device causes the computing device to perform operations comprising:
receiving, by a mobile device, radio frequency (RF) signals from a plurality of RF sources;
determining information associated with the plurality of RF sources;
comparing the determined information with a priori information associated with a set of indoor-only RF sources; and
determining whether the plurality of RF sources include at least one of the set of indoor-only RF sources.

claim.claim-text:
A method, comprising:
receiving, by a mobile device, radio frequency (RF) signals from a plurality of RF sources;
determining information associated with the plurality of RF sources;
comparing the determined information with a priori information associated with a set of indoor-only RF sources; and
determining whether the plurality of RF sources include at least one of the set of indoor-only RF sources.

An article of manufacture including a computer-readable storage medium having instructions stored thereon, execution of which by a computing device causes the computing device to perform operations comprising:
receiving, by a mobile device, radio frequency (RF) signals from a plurality of RF sources;
determining information associated with the plurality of RF sources;
comparing the determined information with a priori information associated with a set of indoor-only RF sources; and
determining whether the plurality of RF sources include at least one of the set of indoor-only RF sources.
